I am deeply grieved,

00:22:14.269 --> 00:22:16.109
Even to death,

00:22:16.109 --> 00:22:20.390
Stay here and keep on the watch with me.

00:22:20.390 --> 00:22:22.230
And going a little way forward,

00:22:22.230 --> 00:22:25.750
He fell face down, praying.

00:22:25.750 --> 00:22:29.230
My Father, if it is possible,

00:22:29.230 --> 00:22:32.829
Let this cup pass away from me,

00:22:32.829 --> 00:22:35.630
Yet not as I will,

00:22:35.630 --> 00:22:38.470
But as you will.

00:22:38.470 --> 00:22:42.710
He returned to the disciples and found them sleeping.

00:22:42.710 --> 00:22:44.869
And He said to Peter,

00:22:44.869 --> 00:22:50.509
Could you not so much as keep on the watch for one hour with me?

00:22:50.509 --> 00:22:54.390
Keep on the watch and pray continually

00:22:54.390 --> 00:22:58.150
So that you may not enter into temptation.

00:22:58.150 --> 00:23:00.829
The Spirit, of course, is eager,

00:23:00.829 --> 00:23:04.799
But the flesh is weak.

00:23:04.799 --> 00:23:07.200
Again, a second time,

00:23:07.200 --> 00:23:09.400
He went off and prayed,

00:23:09.400 --> 00:23:14.200
My Father, if it is not possible for this to pass away,

00:23:14.200 --> 00:23:16.160
Unless I drink it,

00:23:16.160 --> 00:23:19.160
Let your will take place.

00:23:19.160 --> 00:23:23.240
And He came again and found them sleeping

00:23:23.240 --> 00:23:27.279
For their eyes were heavy.

00:23:27.279 --> 00:23:28.720
So leaving them,

00:23:28.720 --> 00:23:32.160
He again went off and prayed for a third time,

00:23:32.160 --> 00:23:37.279
Saying once more the same thing.

00:23:37.279 --> 00:23:41.240
Then He returned to the disciples and said to them,

00:23:41.240 --> 00:23:43.279
At such a time as this,

00:23:43.279 --> 00:23:46.920
You are sleeping and resting.

00:23:46.920 --> 00:23:49.640
Look, the hour has drawn near

00:23:49.640 --> 00:23:52.039
For the Son of Man to be betrayed

00:23:52.039 --> 00:23:54.359
Into the hands of sinners.

00:23:54.359 --> 00:23:57.039
Get up, let us go.

00:23:57.039 --> 00:24:02.619
Look, my betrayer has drawn near.

00:24:02.619 --> 00:24:04.500
While he was still speaking,

00:24:04.500 --> 00:24:08.059
Look, Judas, one of the twelve came

00:24:08.059 --> 00:24:11.779
And with him a large crowd with swords and clubs

00:24:11.779 --> 00:24:16.140
Sent from the chief priests and the elders of the people.

00:24:16.140 --> 00:24:20.299
Now his betrayer had given them a sign, saying,

00:24:20.299 --> 00:24:24.259
Whoever it is I kiss, he is the one.

00:24:24.259 --> 00:24:26.660
Take him into custody.

00:24:26.660 --> 00:24:30.700
And going straight up to Jesus, he said,

00:24:30.700 --> 00:24:36.579
Greetings, Rabbi, and gave him a tender kiss.

00:24:36.579 --> 00:24:39.099
But Jesus said to him,

00:24:39.099 --> 00:24:44.380
Fellow, for what purpose are you present?

00:24:44.380 --> 00:24:47.500
Then they came forward and seized Jesus

00:24:47.500 --> 00:24:49.819
And took him into custody.

00:24:49.819 --> 00:24:52.259
But look, one of those with Jesus

00:24:52.259 --> 00:24:54.779
Reached out his hand and drew his sword

00:24:54.779 --> 00:24:57.299
And struck the slave of the high priest,

00:24:57.299 --> 00:25:02.299
Taking off his ear, then Jesus said to him,

00:25:02.299 --> 00:25:05.299
Return your sword to its place

00:25:05.299 --> 00:25:08.019
For all those who take up the sword

00:25:08.019 --> 00:25:10.420
Will perish by the sword.

00:25:10.420 --> 00:25:13.740
Or do you think that I cannot appeal to my father

00:25:13.740 --> 00:25:18.619
To supply me at this moment more than twelve legions of angels?

00:25:18.619 --> 00:25:22.259
In that case, how would the scriptures be fulfilled

00:25:22.259 --> 00:25:25.779
That say it must take place this way?

00:25:25.779 --> 00:25:29.380
In that hour, Jesus said to the crowds,

00:25:29.380 --> 00:25:32.619
Did you come out to arrest me with swords and clubs

00:25:32.619 --> 00:25:34.660
As against a robber?

00:25:34.660 --> 00:25:38.220
Day after day, I used to sit in the temple teaching

00:25:38.220 --> 00:25:41.579
And yet you did not take me into custody.

00:25:41.579 --> 00:25:44.140
But all of this has taken place

00:25:44.140 --> 00:25:47.980
For the writings of the prophets to be fulfilled.

00:25:47.980 --> 00:25:56.000
Then all the disciples abandoned him and fled.

00:25:56.079 --> 00:25:58.920
Those were significant verses

00:25:58.920 --> 00:26:03.319
Leading up to the two greatest acts of love of all time.

00:26:03.319 --> 00:26:08.000
Jehovah and Jesus cooperated together to undo

00:26:08.000 --> 00:26:13.319
The works of the devil that were initiated back in the garden of Eden

00:26:13.319 --> 00:26:16.480
With Adam and Eve.

00:26:16.480 --> 00:26:20.079
Whether ever you're anointed or the other sheep

00:26:20.079 --> 00:26:24.400
We all have the marvelous hope of everlasting life

00:26:24.400 --> 00:26:32.190
Based on the ransom sacrifice of the perfect man, Jesus.

00:26:32.190 --> 00:26:37.710
We hope all of you enjoy your evening commemorating Jesus' death

00:26:37.710 --> 00:26:40.190
In behalf of all of us.
